    "title": "[MoE] Add RoutingMethodType.Simulated to TRT-LLM FP8/NVFP4 kernel allowlists",
    "user": {
      "login": "jaewonlee-fb",
      "id": 52840625,
      "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjUyODQwNjI1",
